== Chrome ==
* Open ''Settings'' -> ''Privacy and security'' -> ''Security'' -> ''Manage certificates''.
* In the ''Authorities'' tab, click ''Import'' and select the downloaded file.
* Check ''Trust this certificate for identifying websites'' in the upcoming dialog, and click ''OK''.